---
title: Classic New York Style Cheesy Hot Dogs with Fried Onions, Spiced Chips and 'Slaw
description: This Classic New York Style Cheesy Hot Dogs is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W18_UK_F13746-4_Main_add_low-e85717dc.jpg
